tEntry` to use each destination amount, validate sum equals totalAmount, and ensure credits are correct.\n   - Fix `getProfitAndLoss` to sum revenue from credits (positive), expenses from debits, and compute net income as revenue − expenses.\n4. **Run tests after each change** to ensure no regressions.\n5. **Update progress log** after each iteration.\n6. **When all tests pass**, run build and lint to confirm.\n7. **Mark loop complete**.\n\n## Key files\n- `src/ledger.ts` – main implementation.\n- `tests/ledger.test.ts` – test suite.\n\n## Risks & Mitigations\n- *Risk*: Changing sign logic may affect other parts of the code.\n  *Mitigation*: Run full test suite after each modification.\n- *Risk*: Introducing currency validation may require handling accounts without a currency (should default to USD, already set). Ensure default works.\n- *Risk*: Adjusting `splitEntry` could affect existing passing tests.\n  *Mitigation*: Ensure source account existence check remains, and add validation for sum.\n\n## Todo List (to be created via `todowrite`)\n1. Add duplicate account name rejection.\n2. Add currency mismatch validation in `postEntry`.\n3. Fix `getBalance` sign handling.\n4. Fix `getTrialBalance` credit accumulation.\n5. Ensure trial balance totals balance.\n6. Fix `getStatement` date start filter and running balance.\n7. Fix `splitEntry` credit amounts and total validation.\n8. Fix `getProfitAndLoss` revenue sign and net income calculation.\n9. Run full test suite, build, and lint.\n10. Mark loop complete.\n\n---\n","encoding":"utf-8"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","title":".opencode/plans/ralph-plan.md","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/workspace/.opencode/plans/ralph-plan.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1772770293551,"end":1772770293558}}}}
